data.description: Elegant Living at 172 Giordano Mews, Mays Landing, NJ 08330. Step into a world of luxury and comfort with this exquisite 3-bedroom, 3 full bath residence, nestled in the heart of the sought-after Tavistock over 55 community. As the largest model in the vicinity, this home boasts a generous 1,820 square feet of living space, ensuring ample room for relaxation and entertainment. Cul de Sac living with very low through traffic. The home's thoughtful design places the third bedroom complete with a full bath on the second floor, offering privacy and a serene retreat for guests or family. The dining area seamlessly flows into a vast family room, which further opens up to a cook's kitchen. Culinary enthusiasts will be delighted with the 42" cherrywood kitchen cabinets and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, making meal preparations a joy. The master bedroom is nothing short of a sanctuary, featuring an en-suite master bath suite that promises relaxation after a long day. Convenience is key with a first-floor laundry facility and a spacious 2-car garage. Step outside to a covered backyard patio, perfect for alfresco dining or simply soaking in the serene surroundings. The Tavistock community is not just a place to live but a lifestyle. With amenities such as a clubhouse, exercise room, and breathtaking landscapes dotted with multiple ponds teeming with wildlife, every day feels like a vacation. The meticulously maintained curb and sidewalk further enhance the community's charm. But what truly sets this community apart is its spirit. At Tavistock, neighbors don't just live next door; they become lifelong friends, sharing moments and memories. Don't miss out on this opportunity to be a part of a community where life is celebrated, and every day brings new adventures. Welcome to 172 Giordano Mews – where dreams meet reality.
